                </p>
                <p>
                  Be inspired by our executive team as they celebrate our successes and guide our vision for 2026 and beyond.
                </p>
              </div>

              <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4 mt-10">
                <a href="#register" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-8 py-4 bg-vectra-neon hover:bg-emerald-400 text-vectra-dark font-semibold text-lg rounded-full transition-all">
