                <div class="accordion-content">
                  <p>All SKO travel arrangements (both domestic and international) must be booked through Navan. Please follow the link in your confirmation email after registration and look for the SKO pop up.</p>
                  <p class="mt-2 text-amber-700 font-medium">No other travel booked in NAVAN will be accepted.</p>
                  <a href="https://vectra-ai.bravais.com/document/440/preview" target="_blank" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 mt-4 px-5 py-2.5 bg-vectra-blue text-white font-medium rounded-full hover:bg-blue-700 transition">
