                </summary>
                <div class="accordion-content">
                  <p>Check your country's government travel website to see if a travel visa is required for Spain/EU entry. Indicate your visa requirements during registration.</p>
                </div>
              </details>

              <details class="info-accordion">
                <summary>
                  <span>Arrival & Departure Times</span>
                  <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-stone-400 chevron-icon" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"></path></svg>
                </summary>
                <div class="accordion-content">
                  <p><strong>Arrival:</strong> Please arrive by 5:00 PM on Sunday, 8th March. Welcome Reception starts at 7:00 PM.</p>
                  <p class="mt-2"><strong>Departure (EMEA):</strong> Depart Hotel Arts anytime after 12:15 PM on Wednesday, 11th March.</p>
                </div>
              </details>

              <details class="info-accordion">
